Pamaitiro e[[Kubika kweZimbabwe]] (Zimbabwean Cuisine), [[mangayi]]  (boiled dry maize or corn) zvinoreva chibage chakaoma chinofashaidzwa kusvika chaibva. Mangayi anobikwa nechibage chakasvika chikukutu. Panoibva mangayi, rukanda rwekunze rwechibage runotanga kutsemukira; urwu rukanda runofururwa kana pasvika pakudya.

[[Manhuchu]] anosiyana nemangayi pakuti manhuchu chibage chinotanga chadzvurwa kubisa rukanda rwokunze. Vamwe vanoti vasati vabika mangayi vanoaradza ari mumvura kuti apfave arege kuzotora moto wakawanda kana kuti [[nguva]] yakareba kubika.
